2%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evocal%20about%20jet%20trackers%20following%20his%20whereabouts%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Apple%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook%20and%20LVMH%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flouis-vuitton-bernard-arnault-sold-private-jet-people-tracking-twitter-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBernard%20Arnault%20only%20rent%20private%20planes%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20security%20and%20privacy%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFlexjet's%20Praetor%20600%20can%20fly%20up%20to%20about%204%2C600%20miles%2C%20or%20nearly%20eight%20hours%20nonstop.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225312%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20beige%20loungers%20in%20forward%20cabin%20of%20the%20Praetor%20600%20plane.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671288a0a0a0cc14f2221988%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223984%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESibilla%20said%20customers%20use%20fractional%20ownership%20for%20both%20business%20and%20pleasure.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20super-midsized%20category%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflexjet.com%2Ffleet%2Fpraetor-600%2F%3Futm_source%3Dgoogle%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dmid%26utm_content%3Dpraetor%2B600%26gad_source%3D1%26gclid%3DCjwKCAjwjsi4BhB5EiwAFAL0YGuDK6Hg66CPXwmRIMF_AX2SREP8VFXa-ZNEy-mu3sui0TyqNNBKmBoCuiUQAvD_BwE%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejet%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20bigger%20and%20longer-ranged%20than%20the%20midsize%20Praetor%20500%20and%20is%20better%20suited%20for%20longer%20trips.%20It%20can%20connect%20cities%20like%20London%20and%20New%20York%20or%20S%C3%A3o%20Paulo%20and%20Miami%2C%20flying%20about%20700%20miles%20further%20than%20its%20sister%20jet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20Sibilla%20said%20Flexjet's%20Praetor%20600%20is%20frequently%20used%20between%20New%20York%20and%20Palm%20Beach%20in%20Florida%2C%20but%20leisure%20travelers%20also%20commonly%20fly%20it%20to%20ski%20destinations%20like%20Bozeman%2C%20Montana%2C%20and%20Aspen%2C%20Colorado.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Praetor%20600's%20150%20cubic%20feet%20of%20storage%20can%20accommodate%20the%20snowboard%20and%20ski%20gear%20needed%20for%20these%20high-dollar%20vacations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20plane%20can%20carry%20two%20pilots%20and%20up%20to%20nine%20passengers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20full%20interior%20of%20the%20FlexJet%20Praetor%20600.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671288f2fd8ede6c99e3d00c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFlexjet%20has%20an%20interior%20design%20center%20in%20Ohio.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20six%20loungers%20and%20a%20three-person%20divan%20available%20on%20board%2C%20with%20two%20pilots%20in%20the%20cockpit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESibilla%20said%20Flexjet%20has%20customized%20the%20interiors%20of%20its%20aircraft%20with%20different%20color%20schemes%20and%20designs%20to%20give%20its%20customers%20a%20homey%20environment%20and%20bridge%20the%20gap%20between%20fractional%20ownership%20and%20wholly%20owning%20the%20jet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlexjet%20pilots%20are%20specific%20to%20the%20plane's%20tail%20number%20to%20further%20personalize%20the%20fractional%20experience%2C%20as%20well%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20divan%20can%20be%20converted%20into%20a%20bed.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20divan%20converted%20into%20a%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67128971a0a0cc14f22219dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFlyers%20have%20a%20lie-flat%20bed%20option%20on%20the%20Praetor%20600.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20bed%20onboard%20can%20greatly%20increase%20the%20value%20of%20a%20larger%20plane%20like%20the%20Praetor%20600%2C%20especially%20on%20transatlantic%20or%20cross-country%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20individual%20lounges%20can%20also%20be%20adjusted%20into%20twin%20beds%2C%20but%20Sibilla%20said%20the%20seat's%20legrest%20and%20deep%20recline%20are%20often%20comfortable%20enough%20for%20flyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECustomers%20can%20cater%20almost%20any%20food.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223941%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20back%20of%20the%20Praetor%20600%20with%20the%20divan%20in%20couch%20mode%20and%20the%20dining%20table%20set%20up%20next%20to%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671289d801ea6d83dee24370%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222956%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECatering%20was%20set%20up%20to%20demonstrate%20part%20of%20a%20cabin%20server's%20job%2C%20though%20servers%20are%20not%20staffed%20on%20the%20Praetor%20600.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFlexjet%20has%20a%20standardized%20menu%20but%20the%20company%20said%20it%20can%20accommodate%20customer%20requests%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20anything%20from%20five-star%20luxury%20restaurants%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-loves-mcdonalds-afraid-of-being-poisoned-2018-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMcDonald's%20french%20fries.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20can%20eat%20at%20the%20pull-out%20tables%20between%20each%20set%20of%20forward%20and%20aft%20loungers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESibilla%20said%20some%20of%20its%20private%20planes%2C%20like%20the%20Gulfstream%20G450%2C%20automatically%20staff%20a%20%26quot%3Bcabin%20server%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20Flexjet's%20term%20for%20a%20flight%20attendant.%20The%20Praetor%20600%20doesn't%20offer%20servers.%20Its%20galley%20has%20a%20convection%20oven%20and%20other%20equipment%20to%20prepare%20meals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20is%20a%20lavatory%20and%20storage%20room%20in%20the%20back%20of%20the%20jet.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20window%20in%20the%20lavatory.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67128a0e01ea6d83dee2438f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20sink%20and%20mirror%20are%20opposite%20the%20toilet.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bathroom%20was%20surprisingly%20chic%2C%20with%20woodlike%20finishes%2C%20a%20sink%2C%20a%20mirror%2C%20and%20even%20a%20window.%20The%20toilet's%20thick%20cushion%20cover%20is%20distinctive%20from%20commercial%20plane%20bathrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20storage%20room%2C%20accessible%20from%20the%20bathroom%2C%20can%20hold%20snacks%2C%20toiletries%2C%20and%20other%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20cockpit%20has%20advanced%20avionics%20for%20safety%20and%20efficiency.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223697%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cockpit%20of%20the%20Praetor%20600.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67128aa8fd8ede6c99e3d0b3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222954%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20cockpit%20does%20not%20have%20a%20yoke.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Praetor%20600%20has%20an%20advanced%20fly-by-wire%20system%20(meaning%20the%20pilot%20doesn't%20have%20a%20yoke)%20that%20is%20designed%20to%20make%20flying%20easier%20and%20less%20busy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20large%20cockpit%20screens%20aim%20to%20help%20with%20workflow%20and%20situational%20awareness.%20The%20Praetor%20600%20and%20its%20Praetor%20500%20sister%20jet%20have%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20best%20safety%20records%2C%20according%20to%20an%20analysis%20of%20safety%20records%20by%20charter%20broker%20Stratos%20Jet%20Charters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20also%20offers%20inflight%20WiFi%2C%20a%