20pandemic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks-to-buy-market-outlook-september-history-investing-strategy-bmo-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20volatile%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20October%20is%20often%20better%20for%20stocks%2C%20that%20hasn't%20been%20the%20case%20in%20recent%20election%20cycles.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20only%20risen%20once%20in%20October%20ahead%20of%20the%20five%20presidential%20elections%2C%20technical%20strategist%20David%20Keller%20noted%20on%20a%20mid-October%20webinar%20about%20stocks%20and%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20script%20has%20flipped%20so%20far%20this%20fall.%20Stocks%20seem%20to%20have%20missed%20the%20memo%20about%20those%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstockcharts.com%2Ffreecharts%2Fseasonality.php%3Fsymbol%3DSPY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etroubling%20seasonal%20tendencies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20have%20made%20a%20precedent-defying%20run%20to%20new%20highs.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20is%20in%20uncharted%20territory%20after%20steadily%20climbing%20by%208%25%20since%20early%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Keller%20has%20been%20blown%20away%20by%20the%20market's%20return%20in%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%2C%20he%20believes%20investors%20shouldn't%20get%20complacent%20before%20a%20potentially%20tectonic-shifting%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20have%20an%20uptrend%20that%20lasts%20this%20long%2C%20when%20we%20have%20conditions%20that%20get%20this%20positive%2C%20maybe%20we%20start%20to%20think%20of%20contrarian%20signals%20that%20tell%20me%20maybe%20we're%20starting%20to%20rotate%20lower%2C%26quot%3B%20Keller%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20top%20strategist%20at%20Sierra%20Alpha%20Research%2C%20said%20on%20the%20webinar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20consensus%20view%20in%20markets%20is%20that%20there%20aren't%20any%20big%20red%20flags%20for%20stocks%20or%20the%20economy%2C%20though%20huge%20run-ups%20don't%20happen%20otherwise.%20As%20always%2C%20Keller%20said%20it's%20worth%20staying%20on%20guard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20amount%20of%20warning%20you%20often%20get%20between%20the%20peak%20happening%20and%20a%20pretty%20significant%20downturn%20is%20pretty%20limited%2C%20right%3F%20You%20don't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20warning%20before%20that%20tends%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Keller%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20thinking%20of%20ways%20you%20can%20protect%20yourself%20on%20the%20way%20up%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20when%20you%20get%20signs%20of%20exhaustion%20that%20we're%20already%20seeing%20in%20some%20ways%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20where%20I%20think%20it%20can%20behoove%20us%20as%20investors%20to%20try%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20those%20aggressive%20pullbacks%2C%20if%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Keller%20has%20a%20hunch%20%E2%80%94%20based%20on%20various%20technical%20indicators%20that%20he%20follows%20%E2%80%94%20that%20this%20record%20rally%20still%20has%20more%20steam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20volume%20conditions%2C%20the%20breadth%20conditions%2C%20the%20sentiment%20conditions%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20are%20getting%20sort%20of%20near%20that%20overheated%2C%20exhausted%20level%2C%20but%20not%20quite%20signaling%20a%20peak%20just%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20Keller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225da67038-a9c2-4bd9-a975-476028f4a28b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20invest%20for%20a%20Trump%20or%20Harris%20victory%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20past%20performance%20can't%20predict%20the%20future%2C%20as%20the%20gains%20in%20the%20last%20six%20weeks%20prove%2C%20Keller%20still%20thinks%20there's%20value%20in%20knowing%20how%20US%20stocks%20usually%20fare%20following%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20usually%20happens%20in%20an%20election%20year%20is%2C%20November%20and%20December%20are%20pretty%20bullish%20for%20stocks%2C%26quot%3B%20Keller%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhoever's%20elected%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20optimism%20about%20what%20they're%20going%20to%20do%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20talk%20about%20change%20and%20improvement%2C%20and%20that%20optimism%20is%20usually%20reflected%20in%20the%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20substantial%20pullback%20is%20inevitable%2C%20in%20Keller's%20view%2C%20though%20he's%20not%20sure%20whether%20it%20will%20happen%20in%20the%20back%20half%20of%20October%20or%20in%20January%2C%20once%20the%20shine%20from%20the%20incoming%20president%20wears%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20beginning%20of%20the%20next%20year%20is%20where%20it's%20sort%20of%20like%20the%20reality%2C%20the%20newly%20elected%20president%2C%20whoever%20it%20is%2C%20is%20now%20in%20office%2C%20now%20it's%20up%20to%20them%20to%20actually%20implement%20some%20of%20these%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20implementation%2C%20Keller%20shared%20a%20detailed%20outline%20on%20his%20webinar%20of%20how%20certain%20parts%20of%20the%20market%20should%20perform%20under%20Donald%20Trump%20or%20Kamala%20Harris.%20The%20veteran%20strategist%20also%20talked%20about%20what%20he's%20half-jokingly%20calling%20%26quot%3BDave's%20election-proof%20portfolio%26quot%3B%20of%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20if%20I%20want%20to%20guarantee%20that%20it's%20'election-proof%2C'%20but%20I%20like%20to%20focus%20on%20which%20types%20of%20companies%2C%20which%20areas%20of%20the%20market%20stand%20to%20do%20well%2C%20most%20likely%20%E2%80%94%20regardless%20of%20who%20wins%2C%26quot%3B%20Keller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%20are%20Keller's%20best%20ideas%20for%20either%20a%20Trump%20or%20Harris%20win%2C%20plus%20five%20investments%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks-to-buy-election-investing-strategy-donald-trump-kamala-harris-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshould%20be%20fine%20either%20way%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Note%20that%20Keller%20isn't%20a%20financial%20advisor%2C%20so%20these%20calls%20shouldn't%20be%20treated%20as%20official%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20to%20invest%20if%20Donald%20Trump%20wins%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668c46b4268f62ba18a82ee8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Republican%20presidency%20could%20result%20in%20higher%20spending%20on%20national%20defense%2C%20which%20would%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20%3Cstrong%3Edefense%20contractors%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Elike%20Raytheon%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Frtx-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERTX%3C%2Fa%3E)%20or%20General%20Dynamics%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fgd-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGD%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20Keller%20said.%20The%20former%20is%20on%20a%20tear%20lately%20after%20rising%2026%25%20from%20its%20summer%20lows%2C%20and%20the%20latter%20posted%20a%20solid%20run%20of%207%25%20but%20has%20been%20stuck%20in%20limbo%20for%20the%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndustrials%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20broadly%20may%20also%20benefit%20after%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdigital.fidelity.com%2Fprgw%2Fdigital%2Fresearch%2Fsector%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20the%20market's%20top%20sectors%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months.%20Keller%20said%20some%20of%20this%20strength%20may%20be%20priced%20in%20already%2C%20though%20he%20sees%20the%20group%20succeeding%20under%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETraditional%20energy%20companies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20would%20almost%20certainly%20benefit%20from%20Trump's%20policies%20than%20those%20of%20Harris%2C%20Keller%20said%2C%20though%20oil%20prices%20and%20the%20trajectory%20of%20economic%20growth%20would%20likely%20be%20even%20bigger%20drivers.%20This%20sector%20has%20been%20the%20worst%20performer%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20so%20far%20this%20year%2C%20though%20the%20technical%20strategist%20said%20its%20relative%20strength%20may%20improve%20under%20a%20different%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPharmaceutical%20stocks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20might%20also%20find%20Trump%20more%20sympathetic%20to%20their%20cause%20than%20Harris%2C%20as%20the%20regulatory%20backdrop%20for%20them%20would%20likely%20be%20much%20more%20lenient%2C%20Keller%20said.%20He'd%20play%20the%20trend%20through%20a%20fund%20like%20the%20SPDR%20S%26amp%3BP%20Pharmaceuticals%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fspdr-sp-pharmaceuticals-etf-us78464a7220%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EXPH%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20especially%20since%20the%20once-ignored%20healthcare%20sector's%20technical%20trend%20has%20improved%20significantly%20since%20early%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20to%20invest%20if%20Kamala%20Harris%20wins%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kamala%20Harris%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67054824198738e3a70f05b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDemocratic%20presidential%20nominee%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20speaks%20during%20a%20rally%20at%20the%20Dort%20Financial%20Center%20on%20October%2004%2C%202024%20in%20Flint%2C%20Michigan.%20Harris%20had%20two%20campaign%20stops%20in%20Michigan%20today%20as%20she%20goes%20head-to-head%20with%20Republican%20presidential%20nominee%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20who%20had%20and%20event%20in%20the%20swing%20state%20yesterday%2C%3Cp%3EScott%20Olson%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERenewable%20energy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20%3Cstrong%3Esolar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20stocks%20seem%20like%20logical%20investments%20if%20Harris%20gets%20a%20promotion%20from%20vice%20president%2C%20Keller%20said.%20These%20companies%20have%20been%20shockingly%20weak%20under%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20as%20the%20Invesco%20Solar%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Finvesco-solar-etf-us46138g7060%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETAN%3C%2Fa%3E)%20has%20shed%20nearly%2070%25%20of%20its%20value%20from%20its%20peak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20far%20from%20a%20cure-all%2C%20a%20Harris%20win%20could%20give%20a%20boost%20to%20this%20beleaguered%20industry%2C%20Keller%20said.%20The%20group's%20technicals%20would%20have%20to%20improve%20substantially%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20strategist%20is%20watching%20to%20see%20if%20solar%20ETFs%20can%20reclaim%20their%20200-day%20moving%20averages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20these%20companies%20should%20do%20better%20under%20that%20administration%2C%20I'm%20a%20little%20bit%20skeptical%2C%20just%20given%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20haven't%20done%20as%20well%20up%20until%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Keller%20said.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20technical%20perspective%2C%20I%20still%20think%20they%20have%20quite%20a%20bit%20to%20prove%20before%20I%20think%20they're%20a%20decent%20bet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EElectric%20vehicles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20are%20another%20industry%20that%20should%20be%20pulling%20for%20Harris%2C%20Keller%20said.%20Ironically%2C%20he%20cited%20Tesla%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Ftsla-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETSLA%3C%2Fa%3E)%20as%20a%20prime%20example%20of%20a%20big%20winner%20under%20this%20scenario%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-trump-america-super-pac-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%20is%20all%20aboard%20the%20Trump%20train%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%205-part%20'election-proof'%20portfolio%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222779%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harris%20Trump%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e1f1b6bf0250c214927ae6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221976%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20and%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20are%20locked%20in%20a%20competitive%20race%20in%20Pennsylvania.%3Cp%3EDemetrius%20Freeman%2FThe%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20who%20are%20tuned%20out%20of%20politics%20or%20don't%20want%20to%20speculate%20on%20this%20November's%20winner%20can%20instead%20put%20their%20money%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks-to-buy-election-investing-strategy-donald-trump-kamala-harris-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparts%20of%20the%20market%20that%20should%20be%20fine%20either%20way%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20Keller's%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHomebuilders%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20are%20the%20first%20such%20area%2C%20as%20the%20group%20should%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-mortgage-rates-outlook-prediction-top-cities-homebuyers-owners-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebenefit%20from%20lower%20interest%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20cause%20demand%20for%20new%20houses%20to%20rise.%20Keller%20cited%20the%20SPDR%20S%26amp%3BP%20Homebuilders%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fspdr-sp-homebuilders-etf-us78464a8889%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EXHB%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20the%20iShares%20US%20Home%20Construction%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fishares-us-home-construction-etf-us4642887529%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EITB%3C%2Fa%3E)%20as%20viable%20ways%20to%20play%20this%20red-hot%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETechnology%20stocks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20are%20also%20worth%20sticking%20with%2C%20Keller%20said%2C%20even%20though%20they've%20had%20a%20massive%20run%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20Semiconductor%20companies%20and%20technology%20giants%20like%20Alphabet%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fgoogl-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGOOGL%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20Meta%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fmeta-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMETA%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20and%20Microsoft%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fmsft-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMSFT%3C%2Fa%3E)%20are%20among%20his%20favorite%20ideas%20here%2C%20even%20though%20they're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-search-antitrust-case-doj-remedy-alphabet-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edealing%20with%20regulatory%20scrutiny%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20may%20not%20be%20going%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20more%20of%20a%20broader%20play%2C%20particularly%20a%20play%20on%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Keller%20said.%20%26quot%3BSemiconductors%20are%20probably%20the%20best%20way%20to%20think%20of%20it%2C%20because%20you're%20getting%20exposure%20to%20those%20major%20players.%20Any%20sort%20of%20improvement%20in%20AI%20is%20going%20to%20be%20driven%20by%20semiconductors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-stocks-to-buy-utilities-investing-strategy-advice-goldman-sachs-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eless-heralded%20way%20to%20play%20the%20AI%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20the%20%3Cstrong%3Eutility%20companies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20that%20provide%20their%20power.%20Utilities%20happen%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdigital.fidelity.com%2Fprgw%2Fdigital%2Fresearch%2Fsector%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eby%20far%20the%20best-performing%20sector%20in%20the%20last%20three%20months%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Keller%20noted%20that%20the%20defensive%20group%20tends%20to%20be%20less%20volatile%20with%20high%20dividend%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%