udy%20suggests%20they%20may%20not%20help%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20cardiovascular%20issues%20like%20heart%20disease.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20found%20that%20standing%20for%20more%20than%20two%20hours%20a%20day%20may%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20circulation%20issues.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20into%20the%20pandemic%2C%20my%20husband%20bought%20us%20a%20convertible%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-standing-desk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estanding%20desk%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20were%20both%20working%20from%20home%2C%20and%20aside%20from%20our%20daily%20jogs%20together%2C%20we%20were%20slouching%20in%20our%20respective%20work%20corners%20for%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuddenly%2C%20more%20and%20more%20of%20my%20coworkers%20were%20towering%20in%20their%20Zoom%20calls.%20We%20made%20small%20talk%20about%20how%20our%20new%20standing%20desks%20helped%20with%20our%20posture%20and%20prevented%20us%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-tried-being-more-active-at-work-was-less-productive-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esitting%20all%20day%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20hasn't%20died%20down.%20The%20market-research%20firm%20Global%20Market%20Insights%20estimated%20that%20the%20standing-desk%20market%20was%20valued%20at%20%247.8%20billion%20in%202023%20and%20could%20increase%20by%205.5%25%20annually%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%20Top%20retailers%20like%20Autonomous%2C%20FlexiSpot%2C%20and%20Uplift%20generate%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20revenue%20each%20year.%20In%20its%20branding%20materials%2C%20Autonomous%20suggests%20that%20%26quot%3Bby%20promoting%20movement%2C%20these%20desks%20help%20you%20stay%20active%20and%20prevent%20pain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20a%20while%2C%20instead%20of%20hitting%20the%20button%20to%20elevate%20my%20desk%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20sitting%20all%20day%20after%20my%20morning%20workout.%20While%20some%20of%20my%20colleagues%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-things-that-happened-after-i-stood-for-3-hours-a-day%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efelt%20more%20energized%20standing%20at%20their%20desks%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20three%20hours%2C%20I%20did%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fije%2Farticle%2F53%2F6%2Fdyae136%2F7822310%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20on%20Thursday%20confronted%20my%20conundrum.%20Ultimately%2C%20it%20suggests%20that%20if%20you're%20using%20a%20standing%20desk%20to%20feel%20more%20active%20and%20boost%20your%20health%2C%20the%20trick%20is%20to%20actually%20use%20it%20to%20%3Cem%3Emove%3C%2Fem%3E%20more%2C%20frequently%20standing%20and%20sitting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20data%20from%20more%20than%2080%2C000%20adults%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20the%20researchers%20found%20that%20simply%20standing%20didn't%20necessarily%20help%20get%20people's%20blood%20circulating.%20They%20also%20suggest%20that%20standing%20all%20day%20%E2%80%94%20without%20moving%20around%20%E2%80%94%20may%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20circulatory%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2225df6fac-c6ed-45a7-ab87-bff83d4930d0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESitting%20or%20standing%20for%20over%202%20hours%20may%20not%20be%20good%20for%20health%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%2C%20led%20by%20researchers%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Sydney%2C%20studied%20data%20on%2083%2C013%20adults%20in%20the%20UK%20Biobank%2C%20a%20large%20database%20with%20information%20about%20people's%20genetics%2C%20lifestyle%2C%20and%20health.%20The%20participants%20wore%20accelerometer%20devices%20on%20their%20wrists%20to%20track%20their%20movements%20for%20one%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20concluded%20that%20sitting%20for%2010%20to%2012%20hours%20a%20day%20was%20associated%20with%20an%20increased%20risk%20of%20cardiovascular%20and%20orthostatic%20circulatory%20disease%2C%20such%20as%20varicose%20veins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStanding%20for%20two%20hours%20a%20day%20wasn't%20associated%20with%20a%20reduced%20risk%20of%20cardiac%20conditions%20like%20heart%20failure%2C%20stroke%2C%20or%20heart%20disease%20%E2%80%94%20it%20didn't%20seem%20to%20have%20much%20of%20an%20effect%20on%20cardiovascular%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20did%20find%20that%20standing%20for%20two%20hours%20straight%20was%20associated%20with%20a%20higher%20risk%20of%20orthostatic%20circulatory%20disease%2C%20increasing%20by%2011%25%20every%20additional%2030%20minutes.%20The%20authors%20suggested%20that%20standing%20for%20too%20long%20every%20day%20could%20lead%20to%20long-term%20issues%20with%20blood%20circulation%2C%20such%20as%20venous%20ulcers%20and%20swollen%20veins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b8e299b-9168-4df9-be6f-5275cf2ba174%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20best%20to%20move%20throughout%20the%20day%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDesks%20that%20let%20you%20switch%20between%20standing%20and%20sitting%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-standing-desk-converter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estanding-desk%20converters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20can%20help%20you%20change%20up%20how%20you%20work%20without%20committing%20to%20one%20position%20all%20day.%20Home-office%20upgrades%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ffitness%2Fbest-under-desk-treadmills%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunder-desk%20treadmills%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20also%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20squeeze%20in%20movement%20throughout%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20researchers%20have%20recommended%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaily-exercise-prevent-death-sitting-all-day-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalking%20for%2022%20minutes%20a%20day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20can%20be%20incorporated%20into%20doing%20household%20chores%20or%20taking%20the%20st