ies%20tend%20to%20move%20to%20East%20Jackson%2C%20which%20is%20conveniently%20located%20near%20the%20town%20square.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jacksonholerealestatesearch.com%2Fexplore-jackson-hole%2Ftown-of-jackson%2Feast-jackson%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESotheby's%20International%20Realty%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20area%20has%20a%20mix%20of%20condos%2C%20townhouses%2C%20and%20single-family%20homes%20costing%20as%20much%20as%20%248.7%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou'll%20find%20young%20families%20that%20ride%20their%20e-bikes%20to%20work%20and%20to%20get%20ice%20cream%20in%20the%20summer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFrom%20Wilson%20to%20Teton%20Village%2C%20the%20other%20parts%20of%20Jackson%20Hole%20are%20more%20remote%20%E2%80%94%20and%20expensive.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20modern%20mansion%20on%20the%20left%20with%20rocks%20and%20grass%20in%20the%20foreground%20and%20hills%20and%20mountains%20in%20the%20background%20on%20a%20cloudy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670d4236a70318649281a3c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20mansion%20sits%20on%20a%20hill%20in%20Jackson%20Hole.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20richest%20residents%20in%20Jackson%20Hole%20tend%20to%20live%20in%20the%20more%20remote%20areas%20around%20Jackson%20in%20the%20greater%20Jackson%20Hole%20region%3A%20Kelly%2C%20Moose%2C%20Teton%20Village%2C%20and%20Wilson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaack%20told%20BI%20that%20Teton%20Village%20and%20Wilson%20typically%20have%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20expensive%20homes%20in%20Jackson%20Hole.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20two%20areas%20are%20popular%20due%20to%20their%20more%20quiet%20nature%20as%20well%20as%20being%20outside%20of%20the%20now%20traffic-filled%20town%20of%20Jackson%2C%26quot%