rity%20procedures%2C%20all%20passengers%20had%20to%20be%20deplaned%20as%20the%20local%20authorities%20followed%20necessary%20procedures.%20We%20request%20your%20understanding%20as%20our%20team%20on%20the%20ground%20did%20everything%20possible%20to%20reduce%20the%20inconvenience%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20airline%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Akasa%20Air%20flight%20from%20Bengaluru%20to%20Mumbai%20got%20a%20bomb%20threat%20shortly%20before%20departure.%20The%20airline%20in%20a%20statement%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFlight%20QP%201366%2C%20flying%20from%20Bengaluru%20to%20Mumbai%20on%20Friday%2C%20received%20a%20security%20alert%20shortly%20before%20departure.%20However%2C%20the%20plane%20was%20thoroughly%20checked%20for%20security%20at%20Mumbai%20airport%20as%20per%20SOP.%20No%20objectionable%20items%20of%20any%20kind%20were%20found.%20After%20this%2C%20the%20plane%20was%20given%20NOC%20for%20flight%20after%20the%20security%20check.%20Late%20Friday%20evening%2C%20the%20plane%20took%20off%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20Bengaluru%20with%20a%20delay%20of%20several%20hours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Monday%2C%20at%20least%2050%20flights%20have%20received%20such%20threats%2C%20prompting%20the%20civil%20aviation%20ministry%20and%20authorities%20to%20put%20in%20place%20stricter%20norms%20to%20deal%20with%20such%20situations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-year-flight-ban-for-hoax-callers-say-sources-amid-bomb-threat-to-airlines-6803649%5C%22%3ESources%20earlier%20told%20NDTV%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20airlines%20gave%20inputs%20on%20the%20situation%20and%20the%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20(DGCA)%20suggested%20that%20several%20steps%20will%20be%20taken%20like%20putting%20hoax%20callers%20on%20the%20no-fly%20list%20for%20five%20years.%20The%20airlines%20suggest%20that%20the%20losses%20borne%20by%20them%20due%20to%20fake%20bomb%20threats%20should%20be%20recovered%20from%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C