n%20a%20'mega-bubble'%20with%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20ahead%20of%20fundamentals%20by%20at%20least%2025%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22trader%20nyse%20angry%20surprised%20market%20crash%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5cd5b278021b4c1e4c41a389%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%20%2F%20Spencer%20Platt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EEconomist%20David%20Rosenberg%20warns%20the%20stock%20market%20is%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bmega-bubble.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERosenberg%20cites%20high%20valuations%2C%20investor%20positioning%2C%20and%20sentiment%20as%20warning%20signs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDespite%20recent%20market%20gains%2C%20Rosenberg%20predicts%20a%20recession%20and%20advises%20caution%20in%20investing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20tempting%20time%20to%20jump%20into%20the%20stock%20market.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20continues%20to%20register%20new%20highs%20and%20has%20climbed%20an%20incredible%2023%25%20so%20far%20this%20year.%20That's%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20a%2022%25%20gain%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20isn't%20the%20time%20for%20greed%2C%20says%20famed%20economist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-recession-labor-market-revisions-rate-cuts-rosenberg-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDavid%20Rosenberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20notes%20to%20clients%20this%20month%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Rosenberg%20Research%2C%20who%20called%20the%202008%20recession%2C%20warned%20that%20the%20market%20is%20overvalued%2C%20eventually%20setting%20investors%20up%20to%20get%20burned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20mother%20of%20all%20momentum-driven%20stock%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20an%20October%209%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20this%20mega-bubble%20pops%2C%20it%20will%20be%20spectacular%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%20on%20October%2018.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20no%20time%20to%20chase%20momentum%20or%20the%20herd%20mentality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosenberg%20said%20a%20large%20reason%20for%20his%20bearish%20outlook%20is%20a%20trifecta%20of%20measures%20sitting%20two%20standard%20deviations%20outside%20of%20average%20values%3A%20positioning%20in%20stocks%2C%20market%20valuations%2C%20and%20investor%20sentiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20didn't%20cite%20specific%20measures%20in%20his%20notes%2C%20many%20widely%20followed%20indicators%20corroborate%20these%20assertions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20investor%20positioning%2C%20here's%20household%20equity%20ownership%20as%20a%20percentage%20of%20assets%20as%20of%20the%20start%20of%20this%20year.%20North%20of%2040%25%2C%20it%20exceeds%20levels%20reached%20during%20the%20dot-com%20bubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222360%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22household%20equity%20allocation%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6685bce81f0c1cd6d7318c30%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221126%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESmead%20Capital%20Management%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20valuations%2C%20there%20are%20a%20myriad%20of%20different%20gauges%2C%20but%20two%20common%20ones%20to%20consider%20are%20the%20Shiller%20cyclically%20adjusted%20price-to-earnings%20ratio%20and%20the%20ratio%20of%20the%20Wilshire%20500-to-GDP%2C%20shown%20below%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22shiller%20pe%20ratio%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6712c3d301ea6d83dee28cdb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22380%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGuruFocus%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22total%20market%20cap%20to%20gdp%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6712c3adfd8ede6c99e418bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22380%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGuruFocus%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20many%20measures%20of%20investor%20sentiment.%20One%20popular%20indicator%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aaii.com%2Flatest%2Farticle%2F239694-aaii-sentiment-survey-pessimism-spikes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAAII%20Sentiment%20Survey%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20of%20Thursday%2C%2045.5%25%20of%20its%20respondents%20characterized%20themselves%20as%20bullish%2C%20above%20the%20historical%20average%20of%2037.5%25.%20Almost%20half%20of%20respondents%2C%20however%2C%20said%20they%20think%20the%20market%20is%20overvalued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20Rosenberg's%20measure%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20is%20at%20least%2025%25%20higher%20than%20where%20fundamentals%20suggest%20it%20should%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrices%20have%20outpaced%20earnings%20growth%20in%20the%20past%20year%20and%20if%20this%20were%20a%20classic%20earnings-driven%20rally%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20would%20be%20sitting%20near%204%2C600%2C%20not%20at%205%2C751%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenberg%20said%20in%20the%20October%209%20note.%20%26quot%3BNot%20only%20that%2C%20but%20analyst%20EPS%20revisions%20have%20been%20squarely%20to%20the%20downside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20risen%20to%205%2C864.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosenberg's%20bearish%20views%20on%20the%20market%20come%20alongside%20a%20pessimistic%20view%20of%20the%20economy.%20He%20said%20an%20expectation-beating%20September%20jobs%20report%20was%20an%20outlier%20in%20a%20downward%20trend%2C%20and%20he%20still%20expects%20a%20recession%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22defdb45d-ba91-4e39-8f1f-99b2833d082b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERosenberg's%20views%20in%20context%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bearish%20economist%20has%20been%20calling%20for%20a%20recession%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20now%2C%20and%20has%20warned%20at%20various%20points%20of%20an%20overvalued%20stock%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20market%20has%20soared%2C%20outperforming%20the%20expectations%20of%20even%20the%20most%20bullish%20strategists%20on%20Wall%20Street%2C%20and%20the%20economy%20has%20continually%20shown%20resilience%20despite%20interest-rate%20hikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20signs%20of%20weakness%20are%20emerging%20as%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20trends%20upward%20and%20job%20openings%20and%20new%20hires%20drop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Reserve%20has%20started%20to%20take%20action%20to%20prevent%20further%20slowing%20by%20cutting%20interest%20rates%20by%2050%20basis%20points%20in%20September.%20But%20it's%20still%20not%20clear%20whether%20the%20economy%20is%20at%20the%20start%20of%20a%20new%20business%20cycle%2C%20or%20whether%20it%20will%20buckle%20under%20the%20weight%20of%20elevated%20rates%20and%20plunge%20into%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosenberg%20thinks%20the%20latter%20scenario%20is%20more%20likely%2C%20and%20therefore%20cautioned%20investors%20about%20investing%20at%20this%20stage%20of%20the%20bull%20market%2C%20after%20such%20an%20aggressive%20rally%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BManaging%20money%20means%2C%20at%20all%20times%2C%20preserving%20capital%20while%20capturing%20part%20of%20the%20upside%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenberg%20wrote%20in%20the%20October%2018%20note.%20%26quot%3BJ.P.%20Morgan%20reportedly%20once%20commented%20that%20he%20got%20wealthy%20not%20by%20buying%20at%20the%20lows%20and%20selling%20at%20the%20highs%2C%20but%20rather%20by%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20middle%2060%25%20of%20the%20bull%20market.%20We%20are%20well%20past%20that%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-economist-who-called-2008-recession-mega-bubble-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729328401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6712b7b501ea6d83dee286c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-economist-who-called-2008-recession-mega-bubble-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20mother%20of%20all%20momentum-driven%20stock%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20David%20Rosenberg.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-economist-who-called-2008-recession-mega-bubble-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Venture%20capital%20is%20going%20to%20war%20over%20the%20election.%20Here's%20the%20data%20to%20prove%20it.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Keith%20Rabois%2C%20Vinod%20Khosla%2C%20Marc%20Andreessen%2C%20Reid%20Hoffman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67118197fd8ede6c99e399cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECharles%20Eshelman%2FGetty%2C%20Taylor%20Hill%2FGetty%2C%20Stefanie%20Keenan%2FGetty%2C%20Invision%2FGetty%2C%20Tyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EVCs%20are%20lobbing%20cash%20at%20the%20presidential%20election%20and%20key%20congressional%20races%2C%20FEC%20data%20shows.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20most%20VCs%20favored%20Democrats%2C%20a16z's%20crypto%20giving%20dwarfed%20all%20other%20donations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20top%20individual%20donor%20was%20Greylock%20partner%20Reid%20Hoffman%2C%20who%20pledged%20support%20for%20Kamala%20Harris.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAmerica%20is%20bitterly%20divided%20over%20politics%2C%20and%20the%20tech%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20once%20portrayed%20as%20a%20liberal%20bastion%20%E2%80%94%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felection-a-distraction-silicon-valley-wants-to-be-over-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20different.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Among%20the%20sector's%20investor%20class%2C%20these%20disputes%20typically%20play%20out%20behind%20closed%20doors%2C%20with%20checkbooks%20rather%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-political-divide-twitter-elon-musk-kamala-harris-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eangry%20social%20media%20posts%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20election%20cycle%2C%20investors%20at%20the%20top%20venture%20capital%20firms%20have%20plowed%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20into%20the%20election%2C%20both%20backing%20their%20favored%20political%20candidates%20and%20just%20cannily%20promoting%20commercial%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20trawled%20political%20donation%20data%20released%20by%20the%20Federal%20Elections%20Commission%20to%20see%20how%20employees%20at%20VC%20firms%20have%20donated%20by%20candidates%20and%20political%20entities%20as%20the%20hotly%20contested%20race%20enters%20its%20final%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20is%20limited%2C%20focusing%20only%20on%20a%20subjective%20grouping%20of%2010%20high-profile%20firms%2C%20and%20cutting%20off%20at%20varying%20points%20over%20the%20summer.%20More%20recent%20FEC%20donor%20data%20will%20be%20released%20in%20the%20days%20and%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20the%20November%205%20general%20election%2C%20often%20the%20most%20turbulent%20time%20in%20any%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sheer%20volume%20of%20donations%20captured%20in%20the%20FEC%20filings%20underscores%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20tech%20constituency%20in%20the%20political%20arena%2C%20how%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20elite%20has%20embraced%20politics%20of%20late%2C%20and%20just%20how%20flooded%20by%20money%20modern%20American%20politics%20has%20become.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dd94bff4-8a0b-4fe4-8f40-59db1deb3131%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20big%20spenders%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F8qqk6%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Donations%20by%20venture%20capital%20firm%20employees%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22470%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20venture%20capitalists%2C%20talking%20politics%20can%20invite%20scrutiny%20%E2%80%94%20or%20worse%2C%20turn%20off%20founders%20seeking%20funds%20for%20what%20might%20be%20the%20next%20big%20thing.%20It's%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20why%20many%20firms%20won't%20take%20positions%20on%20political%20issues%20or%20push%20a%20candidate%20on%20their%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20that%20hasn't%20stopped%20individual%20investors%20from%20voting%20with%20their%20dollars%2C%20many%20VC%20firms%20are%20quick%20to%20point%20out%20that%20donations%20do%20not%20represent%20the%20organization's%20political%20stance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExcept%20when%20they%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndreessen%20Horowitz%2C%20or%20a16z%2C%20is%20the%20sole%20firm%20in%20our%20dataset%20to%20make%20political%20contributions%20directly.%20In%20this%20election%20cycle%2C%20it%20contributed%20%2447%20million%20to%20groups%20working%20to%20elect%20blockchain-friendly%20candidates%2C%20including%20Fairshake%2C%20a%20titanic%20crypto-industry%20backed%20super%20PAC.%20The%20firm%20is%20all-in%20on%20crypto%2C%20investing%20in%20Solana%20and%20Yuga%20Labs%2C%20and%20launched%20a%20%244.5%20billion%20investment%20fund%20focused%20on%20this%20area%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20names%20of%20the%20firm's%20founders%2C%20Marc%20Andreessen%20and%20Ben%20Horowitz%2C%20also%20appear%20on%20filings%20for%20donations%20to%20these%20groups%2C%20a16z%20says%20on%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fa16zcrypto.com%2Fposts%2Farticle%2Fcontributing-to-fairshake-pac%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20these%20contributions%20come%20from%20the%20firm%2C%20not%20the%20founders%20personally.%20Though%20the%20distinction%20a16z%20draws%20between%20itself%20and%20its%20founders%20might%20be%20slightly%20artificial%2C%20given%20Andreessen%20and%20Horowitz%20created%2C%20own%2C%20and%20named%20the%20firm%20after%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20the%20brouhaha%20about%20Andreessen%20and%20Horowitz%20putting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-vcs-in-silicon-valley-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emillions%20of%20dollars%3C%2Fa%3E%20behind%20Trump's%20latest%20bid%20for%20the%20White%20House%20and%20Horowitz%20hedging%20his%20bets%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fread-ben-horowitzs-email-a16z-saying-plans-donate-kamala-harris-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20planned%20donation%20to%20Harris%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20data%20shows%20the%20two%20are%20a%20rare%20breed%20among%20venture%20investors%3A%20relatively%20bipartisan%20donors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHorowitz%20sent%20roughly%2059%25%20of%20his%20personal%20political%20contributions%20to%20Republicans%20and%20a%20little%20under%2040%25%20to%20Democrats%2C%20while%20Andreessen%20more%20strongly%20favored%20Republicans%20this%20election%20cycle%2C%20with%2064%25%20of%20his%20donations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20time%20period%20covered%20by%20the%20data%2C%20a16z%20even%20eclipsed%20Greylock%2C%20where%20outgoing%20partner%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-billionaires-investors-kamala-harris-mark-cuban-reid-hoffman-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDemocrat%20megadonor%3C%2Fa%3E%20Reid%20Hoffman%20has%20personally%20pumped%20nearly%20%2430%20million%20in%20recorded%20donations%20into%20the%20presidential%20election%20and%20key%20congressional%20races.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20at%20Founders%20Fund%2C%20which%20has%20backed%20SpaceX%20and%20Palantir%2C%20are%20nearly%20100%25%20Republican%20in%20donations%2C%20though%20the%20bulk%20of%20contributions%20came%20from%20Keith%20Rabois%2C%20who%20left%20the%20firm%20in%20January%20to%20rejoin%20Khosla%20Ventures.%20Employees%20of%20venerable%20firm%20Kleiner%20Perkins%20are%20the%20opposite%2C%20giving%20almost%20entirely%20to%20Democratic%20causes%2C%20as%20is%20the%20case%20for%20Y%20Combinator%2C%20the%20colossal%20startup%20accelerator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%2C%20Sequoia%20Capital%20is%20largely%20bipartisan.%20Unlike%20a16z%2C%20its%20biggest%20donors%20are%20largely%20split%20on%20party%20lines.%20Michael%20Moritz%2C%20who%20left%20the%20firm%20midway%20through%20last%20year%20and%20continues%20to%20serve%20as%20an%20advisor%20to%20Sequoia%20Heritage%2C%20its%20wealth%20management%20group%2C%20gives%20to%20Democrats%2C%20while%20Sequoia%20partner%20Shaun%20Maguire%20donates%20to%20Republicans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223ae3c5f1-4f98-4417-8e68-d3e367656034%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumber-crunching%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20candidate's%20campaign%20or%20other%20political%20entity%20receives%20political%20donations%2C%20they%20must%20report%20it%20either%20quarterly%20or%20monthly%20to%20the%20FEC%2C%20along%20with%20information%20about%20the%20donors%2C%20including%20the%20donor's%20employer.%20The%20federal%20agency%20processes%20these%20filings%2C%20before%20releasing%20them%20in%20a%20searchable%20format%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20analyzed%20for%20this%20story%20cuts%20off%20on%20August%2031%20for%20entities%20that%20report%20donations%20on%20a%20monthly%20basis%20(including%20presidential%20campaigns%2C%20national%20party%20committees%2C%20and%20some%20PACs)%2C%20while%20the%20cut-off%20for%20entities%20that%20report%20quarterly%20(including%20Congressional%20committees%20and%20some%20PACs)%20is%20June%2030.%20(The%20filing%20deadline%20for%20Q3%20data%20for%20quarterly%20filing%20entities%20was%20October%2015%2C%20but%20this%20data%20isn't%20yet%20readily%20available%20in%20full%20online.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20selected%2010%20venture%20capital%20firms%20to%20focus%20on%2C%20taking%20into%20account%20fund%20size%20and%20cultural%20and%20industry%20significance.%20The%20list%20encompasses%20employees%20ranging%20from%20general%20partners%20and%20firm%20founders%20to%20marketers%20and%20executive%20assistants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20should%20not%20be%20interpreted%20as%20an%20exhaustive%20accounting%20of%20all%20venture%20capital%20investors'%20donations%20to%20date%2C%20but%20as%20a%20comparative%20analysis%20of%20how%20some%20of%20the%20industry's%20most%20significant%20players%20have%20approached%20political%20giving%20over%20the%20summer%20as%20the%20election%20heated%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20divided%20the%20recipients%20into%20three%20categories%3A%20Democrat-aligned%2C%20Republican-aligned%2C%20and%20unaffiliated%20%E2%80%94%20a%20grouping%20that%20includes%20both%20bipartisan%20groups%20like%20Fairshake%20and%20independents%20like%20West%20Virginia%20senator%20Joe%20Manchin%2C%20as%20well%20as%20organizations%20like%20The%20Lincoln%20Project%2C%20run%20by%20self-described%20Republicans%20but%20in%20practice%20supporting%20Democratic%20causes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22383b71f4-35bb-4d3d-9fd8-a1daae48b9df%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHoffman%20vs.%20Horowitz%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FCemjG%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Big%20political%20donors%20in%20venture%20capital%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22542%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EHoffman%2C%20the%20top%20individual%20donor%2C%20has%20developed%20a%20reputation%20as%20tech's%20Democratic%20Party%20standard-bearer.%20In%20this%20election%20cycle%2C%20records%20show%20his%20efforts%20include%20%242%20million%20to%20help%20fund%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fsaradorn%2F2024%2F01%2F31%2Fbillionaire-reid-hoffman-spent-2-million-on-bidens-new-hampshire-write-in-campaign-fec-records-show%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunusual%20write-in%20effort%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20in%20New%20Hampshire%2C%20and%20millions%20to%20joint%20fundraising%20committees%20for%20Harris%20after%20Biden%20dropped%20out.%20Hoffman%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F12%2F05%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fnikki-haley-reid-hoffman-donation.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egave%20%24250%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20a%20super%20PAC%20supporting%20Nikki%20Haley%2C%20the%20last%20major%20candidate%20to%20challenge%20Trump%20for%20the%20Republican%20nomination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20donors%20more%20closely%20resemble%20Hoffman%20than%20Horowitz%3A%20clearly%20partisan%2C%20with%20an%20overwhelming%20majority%20of%20their%20donations%20going%20to%20support%20one%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVinod%20Khosla%20of%20Khosla%20Ventures%20is%20another%20of%20the%20biggest%20donors%20on%20the%20Democratic%20side%20of%20the%20aisle%2C%20with%20more%20than%20%243%20million%20in%20recorded%20donations%20during%20the%20time%20period%20to%20recipients%20including%20the%20Democratic%20Congressional%20Campaign%20Committee%20and%20Harris'%20presidential%20campaign.%20Khosla's%20giving%20puts%20him%20just%20above%20John%20Doerr%2C%20chairman%20of%20Kleiner%20Perkins%20and%20architect%20of%20cleantech%20investing%2C%20though%20he%20hasn't%20managed%20funds%20for%20the%20firm%20in%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESequoia%20Capital's%20Doug%20Leone%20is%20one%20of%20VC's%20most%20prolific%20GOP-aligned%20political%20donors%2C%20giving%20his%20almost%20%243.8%20million%20to%20the%20National%20Republica