20for%20his%20alleged%20role%20in%20directing%20a%20failed%20plot%20to%20kill%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20who%20holds%20dual%20citizenship%20of%20the%20US%20and%20Canada.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20on%20Thursday%20confirmed%20that%20the%20individual%20named%20in%20the%20US%20Justice%20Department's%20indictment%20was%20%26quot%3Bno%20longer%20an%20employee%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fndtv-explains-gurpatwant-singh-pannun-murder-for-hire-case-ex-spy-vikash-yadav-drug-smuggler-nikhil-gupta-plot-to-kill-khalistani-terrorist-6816220%5C%22%3EVikas%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Vikash%20Yadav%2C%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20special%20cell%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20in%20December%20last%20year%20after%20a%20complaint%20by%20a%20businessman%20from%20Rohini%20in%20north%20west%20Delhi%20and%20a%20chargesheet%20was%20filed%20in%20March%20this%20year.%20Yadav%20got%20bail%20a%20month%20later%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20businessman%20-%20who%20is%20said%20to%20have%20many%20contacts%20in%20west%20Asia%20-%20told%20police%20that%20his%20acquaintance%20had%20introduced%20him%20to%20Vikas%20Yadav%20in%20November%202023%20and%20told%20him%20that%20he%20was%20a%20senior%20government%20officer.%20They%20soon%20shared%20mobile%20numbers%20to%20stay%20in%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20complaint%2C%20Yadav%20often%20asked%20him%20about%20his%20work%20and%20friends.%20The%20former%20government%20employee%20had%20also%20told%20him%20that%20he%20worked%20as%20an%20undercover%20agent.%20But%2C%20he%20never%20shared%20any%20information%20about%20his%20work%20and%20office%2C%20the%20businessman%20told%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2011%2C%20Yadav%20called%20him%20and%20said%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20discuss%20some%20issue%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20come%20to%20Lodhi%20Road%2C%20as%20per%20the%20complaint.%20There%20was%20another%20man%20with%20Yadav%20when%20he%20reached%20the%20location.%20The%20businessman%20claimed%20that%20they%20forcibly%20kidnapped%20him%20and%20took%20him%20to%20a%20flat%20in%20Defence%20Colony%2C%20where%20Yadav%20told%20him%20that%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20had%20given%20him%20a%20contract%20to%20kill%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav's%20associate%20then%20hit%20him%20on%20the%20head%20and%20took%20away%20his%20gold%20chain%20and%20rings%2C%20he%20alleged%2C%20adding%20they%20went%20to%20his%20cafe%20and%20took%20whatever%20cash%20was%20there.%20According%20to%20the%20complainant%2C%20they%20left%20him%20on%20the%20side%20of%20a%20road%20and%20threatened%20him%20with%20a%20dire%20outcome%20if%20he%20complained%20to%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20businessman%20soon%20went%20to%20the%20police%20and%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20or%20FIR%20was%20filed%20in%20the%20case%20under%20the%20sections%20of%20attempt%20to%20murder%2C%20criminal%20conspiracy%20and%20kidnapping.%20Yadav%20and%20his%20associate%20were%20arrested%20on%20December%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20interrogation%2C%20the%20associate%20told%20the%20police%20that%20he%20joined%20the%20conspiracy%20with%20Vikas%20Yadav%20as%20he%20had%20suffered%20losses%20in%20his%20business%20of%20old%20vehicles.%20He%20said%20that%20Yadav%20told%20him%20that%20his%20father%20was%20in%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikas%20Yadav%20said%20that%20he%20planned%20the%20whole%20crime%20the%20day%20he%20met%20the%20businessman.%20Delhi%20Police%20filed%20a%20case%20in%20March%2C%20and%20Vikas%20got%20bail%20in%20April.%20Although%20Vikas%20got%20interim%20bail%20on%20March%2022%2C%20but%20then%20he%20got%20regular%20bail%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS'%20Charges%20Against%20Vikas%20Yadav%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fex-indian-spy-charged-in-us-over-alleged-khalistani-terrorist-murder-plot-report-6815072%5C%22%3EVikas%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20faces%20three%20charges%3A%20conspiracy%20to%20hire%20a%20hitman%2C%20the%20actual%20%26quot%3Bmurder-for-hire%26quot%3B%20plot%2C%20and%20money%20laundering.%20The%20charges%20against%20him%20and%20his%20alleged%20co-conspirator%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20were%20unsealed%20in%20the%20Federal%20Southern%20District%20of%20New%20York%20Court%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20indictment%2C%20Yadav%20was%20the%20alleged%20mastermind%20who%20recruited%20Gupta%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20plot%20in%20exchange%20for%20helping%20him%20get%20criminal%20cases%20against%20him%20dismissed.%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20and%20was%20extradited%20to%20the%20US%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20details%20in%20the%20document%20repeat%20the%20same%20narratives%20made%20in%20earlier%20documents%20filed%20against%20Gupta%2C%20but%20this%20time%2C%20Yadav%20is%20identified%20by%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYadav%20recruited%20Gupta%20to%20orchestrate%20the%20assassination%20of%20the%20Victim%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20that%20under%20Yadav's%20directions%2C%20Gupta%20contacted%20a%20government%20%26quot%3Bconfidential%20source%26quot%3B%20who%20he%20thought%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20criminal%20associate%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20document%2C%20the%20alleged%20plot%20began%20around%20May%206%20last%20year%20with%20Yadav%20sending%20Gupta%20a%20message%20on%20an%20encrypted%20app%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20Vikas%20...%20save%20my%20name%20as%20Aman%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202023%2C%20they%20hired%20a%20%26quot%3Bhitman%26quot%3B%20and%20agreed%20on%20a%20payment%20of%20%24100%2C000%20to%20allegedly%20kill%20the%20%26quot%3Bvictim%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20court%20document%20which%20did%20not%20name%20Pannun%20said.%20Yadav%20and%20Gupta%20arranged%20through%20an%20%26quot%3Bassociate%20of%20Yadav%26quot%3B%20to%20give%20%2415%2C000%20as%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plot%2C%20however%2C%20unravelled%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bhitman%26quot%3B%20they%20hired%20was%20an%20undercover%20US%20law%20enforcement%20officer%2C%20according%20to%20the%2018-page%20court%20document%2C%20which%20also%20included%20a%20photograph%20of%20Yadav%20dressed%20in%20military%20fatigues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20charges%20were%20filed%20a%20day%20after%20an%20Indian%20Enquiry%20Committee%20set%20up%20to%20investigate%20the%20allegations%20visited%20Washington%20to%20discuss%20the%20case%20with%20US%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20last%20year%2C%20US%20federal%20prosecutors%20charged%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20of%20working%20with%20an%20Indian%20government%20employee%20in%20the%20foiled%20plot%20to%20kill%20Pannun%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729323540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2F4tqmje88_fbi-reuters_625x300_30_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvikas-yadav-ex-indian-spy-vikash-yadav-wanted-by-fbi-for-alleged-gurpatwant-singh-pannun-murder-plot-was-arrested-for-delhi-kidnapping-last-year-6824153%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vikas%20Yadav%2C%20a%20former%20Indian%20government%20employee%20on%20the%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation's%20wanted%20list%2C%20was%20arrested%20ten%20months%20ago%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20on%20charges%20of%20attempted%20murder%20and%20kidnapping.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvikas-yadav-ex-indian-spy-vikash-yadav-wanted-by-fbi-for-alleged-gurpatwant-singh-pannun-murder-plot-was-arrested-for-delhi-kidnapping-last-year-6824153%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kiara%20off%20to%20Delhi%20for%20second%20Karwa%20Chauth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729323376000%2C%