ver%20State%20Anthem%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20has%20posed%20a%20series%20of%20questions%20to%20Governor%20RN%20Ravi%20regarding%20a%20missing%20line%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20state%20anthem%20during%20its%20rendition%20in%20an%20event%2C%20indicating%20the%20verbal%20fight%20between%20the%20two%20is%20far%20from%20over.%20He%20also%20criticised%20the%20Governor%20for%20%26quot%3Bvilifying%20the%20Dravidian%20race%26quot%3B%20and%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Bimpose%20Hindi%20everywhere%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20flashpoint%20was%20triggered%20after%20a%20line%20with%20the%20word%20'Dravida'%20was%20skipped%20by%20singers%20during%20the%20event%20presided%20over%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Governor%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20didn't%20you%20correct%20the%20omission%20right%20away%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Stalin%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20accusing%20Mr%20Ravi%20of%20skipping%20mentioning%20the%20%26quot%3BDravidian%20model%20in%20the%20past%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20this%20is%20your%20history%2C%20how%20will%20Tamils%20believe%20this%20omission%20was%20inadvertent%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sentence%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EThekkanamum%20adhil%20sirantha%20Dravida%20nal%20thiru%20naadum%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20was%20missing%20when%20the%20singers%20sang%20the%20anthem%20during%20the%20Doordarshan%20Kendra%20Chennai's%20Hindi%20month%20valedictory%20function.%20Doordarshan%20Tamil%20apologised%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Binadvertent%20mistake%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20said%20singers%20had%20no%20intention%20to%20disrespect%20Tamil%20or%20Tamizh%20Thaai%20Valthu%2C%20the%20state%20song.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmk-stalin-asks-centre-to-recall-tamil-nadu-governor-in-row-over-anthem-6819349%5C%22%3EMK%20Stalin%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20strong%20exception%20to%20the%20omission%20and%20accused%20the%20governor%20of%20insulting%20the%20unity%20of%20the%20country%20and%20the%20people%20of%20different%20races%20living%20in%20the%20land%2C%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20observing%20Hindi%20month.%20He%20said%20that%20a%20person%20who%20doesn't%20abide%20by%20the%20law%20and%20acts%20as%20per%20his%20wishes%20was%20not%20fit%20to%20hold%20that%20office%20and%20wondered%20if%20Mr%20Ravi%20was%20a%20governor%20or%20an%20%26quot%3BAryan%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ravi%2C%20on%20his%20part%2C%20accused%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20making%20a%20racist%20remark%20against%20him.%20He%20said%20the%20allegation%20against%20him%20was%20%26quot%3Bunfortunately%20cheap%20and%20lowers%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20high%20constitutional%20office%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%26quot%3B%20His%20response%2C%20however%2C%20was%20silent%20on%20the%20skipped%20line%20by%20the%20singers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20said%20'It%20is%20unfortunately%20cheap%20for%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20to%20make%20racist%20comments%20against%20a%20Governor%20with%20false%20allegations'.%20Governor%2C%20Tamil%20is%20our%20race!%20It%20is%20our%20lifeblood!%20Tamils%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20gave%20their%20lives%20to%20save%20the%20Tamil%20language.%20It%20is%20the%20soil%20that%20laid%20the%20foundations%20of%20the%20First%20Constitutional%20Amendment%20and%20bears%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Indian%20anti-imposition%20struggle.%20If%20you%20call%20our%20love%20for%20Tamil%20racist%2C%20it's%20an%20honour%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20MK%20Stalin%20hit%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20accused%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20governor%20appointed%20by%20it%20of%20trying%20to%20impose%20%26quot%3BHindi%20with%20the%20policy%20of%20'Hindi%20everywhere%20-%20Hindi%20in%20anything'%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20schemes%20and%20slogans%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20kind%20of%20political%20civilization%20is%20it%20to%20forget%20the%20constitutional%20norms%20and%20talk%20about%20politics%20every%20day%2C%20and%20to%20turn%20the%20Governor's%20House%20into%20a%20political%20office%20-%20and%20to%20vilify%20the%20Dravidian%20race%3F%20What%20kind%20of%20culture%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ravi%20had%20said%20that%20he%20recites%20full%20Tamizh%20Thaai%20Vaazhthu%20at%20every%20function%20and%20he%20does%20so%20with%20%26quot%3Breverence%2C%20pride%20and%20precision%26quot%3B.%20Under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Hon'ble%20Prime%20Minister%20Thiru%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20Central%20government%20has%20proudly%20created%20several%20institutions%20for%20spread%20of%20Tamil%20language%20and%20heritage%20within%20India%20including%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20several%20countries%20of%20the%20world.%20PM%20Modi%20took%20Tamil%20even%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20earlier%20said%20the%20Governor%20should%20step%20down%20as%20he%20had%20failed%20to%20speak%20for%20Tamil%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20intend%20to%20continue%20as%20governor%2C%20I%20request%20you%20to%20free%20yourself%20from%20divisive%20forces%20and%20discharge%20your%20duties%20according%20to%20constitutional%20norms%2C%26quot%3B%20MK%20Stalin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20face-off%20began%20after%20MK%20Stalin%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20emphasising%20that%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20does%20not%20grant%20national%20language%20status%20to%20any%20language%2C%20and%20Hindi%20and%20English%20are%20only%20for%20official%20purposes.%20He%20suggested%20avoiding%20the%20Hindi%20language%20month%20celebration%20in%20non-Hindi-speaking%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20condemned%20the%20celebration%20of%20Hindi%20Month%20valedictory%20function%20along%20with%20the%20Golden%20Jubilee%20celebrations%20of%20Chennai%20Doordarshan.%20In%20response%2C%20Governor%20RN%20Ravi%20said%20that%20Hindi%20should%20not%20be%20viewed%20as%20an%20imposition%20but%20as%20a%20language%20to%20be%20celebrated%20alongside%20other%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Doordarshan%20event%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20golden%20jubilee%20celebrations%20of%20Doordarshan%20Chennai%2C%20which%20commenced%20operations%20in%201975.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20raging%20controversy%2C%20Doordarshan%20Kendra%2C%20Chennai%2C%20said%20the%20line%20was%20%26quot%3Binadvertently%20missed%20due%20to%20a%20distraction%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20apologise%20for%20the%20inadvertent%20mistake.%20There%20was%20no%20intention%20from%20the%20singers%20to%20disrespect%20Tamil%20or%20Tamizh%20Thaai%20Valthu.%20In%20this%20regard%2C%20we%20apologise%20for%20the%20inconvenience%20caused%20to%20the%20Hon'ble%20Governor%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20from%20Doordarshan%20Tamil%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tamizh%20Thaai%20Valthu%20was%20made%20the%20state%20anthem%20after%20MK%20Stalin%20became%20Chief%20Minister%20in%202021.%20The%20song%20was%20authored%20by%20Manonmaniam%20Sundaram%20Pillai.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729319700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fm106lobc_mk-stalin-ians_625x300_29_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftamil-nadu-news%2Fmk-stalin-vs-governor-over-state-anthem-row-imposing-hindi-everywhere-6823551%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20has%20posed%20a%20series%20of%20questions%20to%20Governor%20RN%20Ravi%20regarding%20a%20missing%20line%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20state%20anthem%20during%20its%20rendition%20in%20an%20event%2C%20indicating%20the%20verbal%20fight%20between%20the%20two%20is%20far%20from%20over.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftamil-nadu-news%2Fmk-stalin-vs-governor-over-state-anthem-row-imposing-hindi-everywhere-6823551%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%