%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Week%20After%20Baba%20Siddique's%20Murder%2C%20Son's%20Photo%20Found%20In%20Shooter's%20Phone%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20photo%20of%20Zeeshan%20Siddique%20was%20found%20in%20the%20phone%20of%20one%20of%20the%20men%20who%20shot%20his%20father%2C%20Baba%20Siddique%2C%20last%20Saturday.%20The%20phone%20recovered%20from%20one%20of%20the%20accused%20arrested%20during%20the%20investigation%20of%20the%20murder%20case%20of%20the%20NCP%20leader%20had%20his%20photo%2C%20police%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20sources%2C%20the%20photo%20was%20shared%20with%20the%20accused%20by%20their%20handler%20through%20Snapchat.%20The%20platform%2C%20investigators%20say%2C%20was%20used%20by%20the%20shooters%20and%20conspirators%20in%20the%20case%20to%20send%20messages%20to%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20messages%20were%20deleted%20on%20instruction%20from%20their%20handler%2C%20allegedly%20belonging%20to%20the%20gang%20of%20the%20notorious%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fzeeshan-siddiques-cryptic-post-after-father-baba-siddiques-killing-not-all-that-is-hidden-6822850%5C%22%3ESon's%20Cryptic%20Post%20After%20Baba%20Siddique%20Murder%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddique%20was%20shot%20by%20three%20men%20near%20his%20MLA%20son's%20office%20in%20Nirmal%20Nagar%20in%20Mumbai's%20Bandra%20area%20on%20October%2012.%20The%20Congress-turned-NCP%20leader%20was%20rushed%20to%20nearby%20Lilavati%20Hospital%20where%20he%20was%20declared%20dead.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-more-arrested-in-connection-with-baba-siddiques-murder-total-arrests-now-9-6821359%5C%22%3Epolice%20have%20arrested%20nine%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20including%20two%20of%20the%20three%20shooters%20-%20in%20the%20case%20so%20far.%20Five%20of%20them%20-%20Nitin%20Gautam%20Sapre%20(32)%2C%20Sambhaji%20Kisan%20Pardhi%20(44)%2C%20Pradeep%20Dattu%20Thombre%20(37)%2C%20Chetan%20Dilip%20Pardhi%20and%20Ram%20Fulchand%20Kanoujia%20(43)%20-were%20arrested%20yesterday%20for%20allegedly%20providing%20firearms%20and%20logistical%20support%20to%20the%20shooters.%20Three%20accused%20are%20still%20on%20the%20run%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanoujia%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Panvel%20in%20Raigad%2C%20told%20police%20that%20the%20contract%20to%20kill%20Siddique%20was%20initially%20given%20to%20him%20and%20Sapre%2C%20sources%20said.%20He%20quoted%20a%20whopping%20amount%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20to%20take%20up%20the%20contract%20as%2C%20he%20said%2C%20he%20didn't%20want%20to%20kill%20Siddique%2C%20the%20sources%20added.%20After%20Kanaujia%20and%20Sapre%20backed%20off%2C%20the%20task%20was%20given%20to%20Dharmraj%20Kashyap%2C%20Gurnail%20Singh%20and%20Shivkumar%20Gautam%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%20Kashyap%20and%20Singh%20were%20arrested%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20crime%20while%20Gautam%20managed%20to%20escape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20told%20police%20that%20Shubham%20Lonkar%20-%20who%20was%20an%20alleged%20conspirator%20and%20the%20handler%20of%20the%20shooters%20in%20the%20case%20-%20chose%20Kashyap%20and%20Gautam%20for%20the%20job%20because%20he%20knew%20the%20people%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20would%20not%20know%20about%20Baba%20Siddiqui's%20stature%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20that%20they%20would%20agree%20to%20commit%20the%20murder%20even%20for%20less%20money%2C%20according%20to%20the%20police%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConstable%20With%20Baba%20Siddique%20During%20Shooting%20Incident%20Suspended%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaba-siddiques-2-1-security-team-to-be-questioned-by-crime-branch-6817180%5C%22%3EBaba%20Siddique%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20shot%2C%20he%20had%20only%20one%20police%20constable%20-%20a%20part%20of%20his%20security%20detail%20-%20accompanying%20him%20who%20did%20not%20retaliate%20when%20six%20rounds%20were%20fired%20at%20the%20senior%20politician.%20The%20security%20personnel%20has%20been%20suspended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20constable%20told%20the%20investigators%20that%20he%20failed%20to%20react%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident%20as%20some%20%26quot%3Bchilli-like%20substance%26quot%3B%20had%20entered%20his%20eyes%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20shooters%20and%20a%20co-conspirator%20had%20stationed%20themselves%20close%20to%20Mr%20Siddique's%20waiting%20car%2C%20as%20per%20a%20reconstruction%20of%20the%20assassination.%20As%20the%2066-year-old%20came%20out%20of%20the%20office%20and%20tried%20to%20get%20inside%20the%20car%2C%20the%20killers%20let%20off%20some%20device%20that%20covered%20the%20area%20in%20thick%20smoke.%20Many%20thought%20it%20was%20the%20smoke%20from%20the%20firecrackers%2C%20which%20also%20masked%20the%20noise%20of%20gunshots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaba%20Siddique%20had%20a%20'2%2B1'%20security%20which%20means%2C%20two%20security%20guards%20during%20the%20day%20and%20one%20at%20night.%20When%20he%20went%20to%20Bandra%20East%20on%20October%2012%2C%20he%20had%20two%20security%20guards%20with%20him.%20But%20before%20he%20left%20his%20son's%20office%2C%20around%208%3A30%20pm%2C%20one%20of%20the%20two%20security%20guards%20had%20left%20the%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELawrence%20Bishnoi%20Gang%20Link%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbai%20Crime%20Branch%20is%20also%20probing%20if%20the%20arrested%20accused%20had%20any%20link%20to%20the%20firing%20outside%20actor%20Salman%20Khan's%20Galaxy%20Apartments%20residence%20in%20Mumbai's%20Bandra%20area%20in%20April.%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20had%20taken%20responsibility%20for%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20Siddique's%20murder%2C%20a%20Facebook%20post%20claimed%20the%20Bishnoi%20gang%20was%20behind%20it.%20Hours%20later%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20man%20was%20arrested%20from%20Pune.%20The%20police%20said%20the%20arrested%20man%2C%20Pravin%20Lonkar%2C%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bco-conspirator%26quot%3B%20and%20added%20that%20they%20were%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20his%20brother%2C%20Shubham%20Lonkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E31-year-old%20Bishnoi%20-%20in%20jail%20since%202015%20-%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20running%20a%20trans-national%20crime%20syndicate%20by%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency.%20His%20name%20has%20been%20linked%20to%20several%20high-profile%20murder%20and%20extortion%20cases%20including%20the%202022%20killing%20of%20popular%20Punjabi%20singer%20Sidhu%20Moose%20Wala.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729315320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F3ditb2ao_zeeshan-siddique_625x300_19_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fweek-after-baba-siddiques-murder-his-sons-photo-found-in-shooters-phone-6823280%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20photo%20of%20Zeeshan%20Siddique%20was%20found%20in%20the%20phone%20of%20one%20of%20the%20men%20who%20shot%20his%20father%2C%20Baba%20Siddique%2C%20last%20Saturday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fweek-after-baba-siddiques-murder-his-sons-photo-found-in-shooters-phone-6823280%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'America%20is%20ready%20to%20turn%20the%20page'%3A%20Obama%20throws%20weight%20behind%20Harris%20as%20election%20enters%20final%20stretch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729315091000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114367319%2Cimgsize-680837.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Famerica-is-ready-to-turn-the-page-obama-throws-weight-behind-harris-as-election-enters-final-stretch%2Farticleshow%2F114367206.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%